{"tid":1242573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實雞蛋唔係唔好 但我發左個有關豆漿既夢","createTime":"2019-06-19T06:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T06:26:39.000Z","uid":181162,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2853aae9a3e53387e9b213d94eabbc177fe7bd1b","tid":1242573,"uid":181162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:00:26.000Z","msg":"琴晚好攰好早就訓左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n訓訓下就發左個夢 夢見見返到有個朋友一d經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢讀小學果陣，有次星期五<br />\n佢放左枝豆漿係櫃桶  小學生大頭蝦就唔記得拎走<br />\n星期一返到去成陣枝豆漿已經發臭仲漏哂出黎 <br />\n成個櫃桶都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個班房都臭哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多同學臭到指住我朋友黎鬧<br />\n<br />\n果陣我同佢同班 同埋坐得近好fd <br />\n所以成件事雖然係小學發生 但我好深印象<br />\n就算係小學咁耐 我都記得果陣聞到陣<span style=\"color: red;\">過期乳製品</span>陣臭味我都想喊<br />\n<br />\n大家仲有冇發到咩夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb07bc1c5d4aa8b8d63fe6cc2660e745ec0a076","tid":1242573,"uid":181162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93bbc9460a0052ee3ed7619a7590d4785d435d7d","tid":1242573,"uid":181162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:00:56.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06293f6b1a0b2a74e427b86289b84ef090aa180c","tid":1242573,"uid":181162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:01:30.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c184a8e81ba289dda99f6b88363c96ed3420a255","tid":1242573,"uid":181162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"645bd696dfe8c860938bfd8a5a61be641c5b633a","tid":1242